Name: Kill Fish
About the game: Kill Fish is a game about a man who tries to change and get away from his past, but instead repeats the same mistakes over and over again. Try on the skin of a tired, emaciated and practically lost hope hero, and reveal all the secrets of the mysterious place in which you find yourself. In this game you will find: Hand-drawn graphics Quirky enemy design that will scare and touch High, but always (almost) fair difficulty level A mystical story, the true meaning of which will be hard to unravel
